OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to 'loving father'
OL,4,Cafter crash
OL,6,FThe family of a man who died after
OL,7,Fbeing hit by a motorbike have paid
OL,8,Ftribute to a "devoted husband and
OL,9,Floving father".
OL,11,FLyndon Wright, 68, died after he and a
OL,12,Fwoman were struck by the bike in
OL,13,FClayton-le-Woods, Lancashire, on
OL,14,FThursday 7 August.
OL,16,FThe woman, in her 60s, is in a serious
OL,17,Fbut stable condition in hospital,
OL,18,Fpolice say.
OL,20,FThe motorcyclist, a man in his 50s,
OL,21,Fdied at the scene.
