OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to 'loving father'
OL,4,Cafter crash
OL,6,FIt happened on Preston Road (A6), at
OL,7,Fthe junction with Cloverfield at just
OL,8,Fafter 10.30pm.
OL,10,FLyndon's family, who are being
OL,11,Fsupported by specially trained
OL,12,Fofficers, said: "Lyndon Wright, passed
OL,13,Faway suddenly on 8th August 2025
OL,14,Ffollowing a road traffic collision.
OL,16,F"He was a devoted husband and loving
OL,17,Ffather, who leaves behind his wife,
OL,18,FCarol, his son, James, and many dear
OL,19,Ffriends and family who will miss him
OL,20,Fdeeply."
