OL,3,CFamily pays tribute to 'loving father'
OL,4,Cafter crash
OL,6,FThree men, who were present in the
OL,7,Farea at the time of the collision,
OL,8,Fwere all arrested on suspicion of
OL,9,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,11,FA 53-year-old from Whittle-le-Woods in
OL,12,FLancashire, a 57-year-old man from
OL,13,FMiddlewich, and a 46-year-old man from
OL,14,FCongleton - both in Cheshire - have
OL,15,Fall been released under investigation
OL,16,Fpending further inquiries, police have
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,FLancashire Police officers want to
OL,20,Fhear from any witnesses or anyone with
OL,21,Fdashcam, CCTV or doorbell footage.
